app_details.title: Injector Origin
app_details.description: Injector Origin is more than just an injector app. Dive into our hero guides, packed with valuable tips and tricks to master every hero's abilities and strategies. Elevate your skills and enhance your gaming experience with Injector Origin now!

reviews.content: I like this app but I can't see the mistbender skin on Nana and Wanwan's skins are just standing still like a barbie I hope you can fix this and also, is there anything you can do with the skill icon?? Thanks I love this app so much

hey, just saying that this is currently the best one I've been using since last the last month? i forgot.. i would highly suggest it other than other apps out there that neither is an ad hungry ones but some doesn't work, honestly this is the best one so far but my only issue in this one is the skill icon design and some effects, the skill icon design like vanishes after a few uses of the hero itself, and some some effects are missing, wish to get it fixed but great app so far💛 best one!!

My first problem is, the Obsidian blade recall of Alucard, I cannot inject it into the default recall, instead, it injects into a wrong recall. The second, I'm not satisfied that default skins are more detailed than upgrade skins. I always use a skin of a hero because it has extra attributes. The last one is the notification preparation, it never works. These are only my problems, please fix these and I'll rate 5 stars to satisfy me and the other users and to improve your app.
